  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Season the fish fillets with salt and black pepper.",
    "Brush the grill with olive oil to prevent sticking.",
    "Grill the fish for 4-5 minutes per side, or until cooked through.",
    "Meanwhile, heat the tagine paste in a small saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and garlic to the saucepan and cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Stir in the lime juice and cook for an additional 1-2 minutes.",
    "Serve the grilled fish with the tagine sauce spooned over the top.",
    "Garnish with cilantro and serve immediately."
